title: Juice - Hit the Ground Running
description:
Coming together in 2009, Juice has become a major up-and-coming force in the Toronto music scene. Mixing the roots of Rock/Funk/R&B with Pop melodies and Hip-Hop grooves, Juice will make you get down harder than you ever thought was possible!
